title: The Little Prince (Le Petit Prince) Ep 01-04 Greek Audio
description:
The little prince, who lives on a tiny asteroid with his beloved rose, travels with his only friend, a talking fox, trough the galaxy. He lands at planets where the serpent and its black thoughts are suspected to have arrived earlier, each time inspiring or exacerbating a bitter, needless conflict among its human and/or population(s).
